      <purpose_text>
        <para>When high exception vectors are not selected, holds the vector base address for exceptions that are not taken to Monitor mode or to Hyp mode.</para>

      </purpose_text>
      <purpose_text>
        <para>Software must program VBAR(NS) with the required initial value as part of the PE boot sequence.</para>
